QuestData.Title: The Heads of the SI:7
QuestData.Description: These orcs were murdered in cold-blood by the Alliance down on the coast. We did nothing to provoke them.$B$BTheir deaths should not be in vain, $n. Will you bring them justice?$B$B<Aggra appears as if she can barely contain her rage.>$B$BThere are three SI:7 leaders down there along the beach. Bring me each of their heads.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect the heads of Commander Arrington, Darkblade Cyn, and Alexi Silenthowl.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you, $n. The spirits of the fallen can now be put to rest.
